      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, it has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a reinforced rear subframe. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, complemented by a limited-slip differential that ensures surgical precision through corners. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece with a documented service history and a pristine underside, representing the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated M-division era.",
